- its mysql compatable relational databse engine
- provides 5 times better performance than mysql
- starts with 10gb, scales in 10gb uncrements to 64 Tb(storage auto scaling)
- compute resources can scale up to 32vCPUs and 244Gb of memory
- no push button scaling should be scaled on maintainence window
- maintaines 2 copies of data in each avail zone and 3 minimum avail zones, 6 copies of data
- transparently handle loss of 2 copies of data without affecting database write avail and upto 3 copies
  without affecting read avail.
- storage is self healing
Replicas:
- 2 types of replicas are available
  - aurora replicas(currently 15)
  -mysql read replicas(currently 5)


